{# TITLE: Peter Hyans, MD #}

<p><img src="{{ MEDIA_URL }}/images/plast_hyans_180x257_portrai.jpg" alt="Peter Hyans, MD" width="180" height="257" align="left">Dr. Peter Hyans is a board-certified plastic surgeon with special interests in facial rejuvenation, body contouring, and cosmetic and reconstructive breast surgery.</p>

<p>Dr. Hyans has contributed articles for medical journals and participated in local and national lectures specializing in Plastic and Reconstructive Surgery.</p>
	  	
<p><img src="{{ MEDIA_URL }}/images/plast_hyans_71x107_how_to_f.jpg" alt="How To Find The Best Doctors" width="71" height="107" align="right">Dr. Hyans can also be found in How To Find the Best Doctors: New York Metro Area. Castle Connolly publishes this authoritative guide to finding highly qualified physicians throughout the region. Dr. Hyans has been mentioned in New Jersey Monthly magazine, voted as one of the "Top Docs" by his fellow physicians specializing in Plastic and Reconstructive Surgery.</p>

